OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FThe controversial two-child benefit
OL,7,Fcap appears set to be axed, with both
OL,8,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer and
OL,9,FChancellor Rachel Reeves indicating an
OL,10,Fannouncement in the Budget.
OL,12,FFollowing months of speculation about
OL,13,Fwhether the government will keep the
OL,14,Fcap, scrap it entirely, or partially
OL,15,Flift it, many Labour backbenchers who
OL,16,Fhave been lobbying for the two-child
OL,17,Flimit to be abolished are breathing a
OL,18,Fsigh of relief.
