OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FIt restricts the child tax credit and
OL,7,Funiversal credit (UC) to the first two
OL,8,Fchildren in most households, and only
OL,9,Fapplies to children born after 6 April
OL,10,F2017.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives introduced the
OL,13,Fpolicy in an effort to incentivise out-
OL,14,Fof-work parents into employment,
OL,15,Farguing people on benefits "should
OL,16,Fface the same financial choices about
OL,17,Fhaving children as those supporting
OL,18,Fthemselves solely through work".
OL,20,FHow many children does it affect?
