OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FAxing the cap was not in the Labour
OL,7,Fmanifesto; instead, Starmer promised
OL,8,Fto "develop an ambitious strategy to
OL,9,Freduce child poverty".
OL,11,FJust after Labour won the election
OL,12,Flast July, Starmer suspended seven MPs
OL,13,Fwho voted in favour of an SNP motion
OL,14,Fcalling for the cap to be abolished.
OL,16,FShortly after that, the government
OL,17,Fannounced it was launching a Child
OL,18,FPoverty Taskforce, led by the
OL,19,FEducation Secretary and Work and
OL,20,FPensions Secretary, which would
OL,21,Fdevelop a Child Poverty Strategy.
